@startuml Legal Assist — Process Flow

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #64748B
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #FEF3C7
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #D97706
skinparam ArrowColor #475569
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #EFF6FF
skinparam NoteBorderColor #93C5FD
skinparam PartitionBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam PartitionBorderColor #CBD5E1

title **Legal Assist** — Process Flow\n

|#EFF6FF| **Frontend (React)** |
|#DBEAFE| **API (FastAPI)** |
|#DCFCE7| **Services** |
|#FEE2E2| **External** |

' ═══════════════════════════════════
' FLOW 1: AUTHENTICATION
' ═══════════════════════════════════

|**Frontend (React)**|
start
:User opens app;
:Register / Login;

|**API (FastAPI)**|
:POST /auth/register or /login;

|**Services**|
:AuthService validates credentials
bcrypt hash / verify password;

|**External**|
:MongoDB **users** collection
store or lookup user;

|**Services**|
:Generate **JWT token** (2h expiry);

|**Frontend (React)**|
:Store token in localStorage
Redirect to Upload page;

' ═══════════════════════════════════
' FLOW 2: DOCUMENT UPLOAD
' ═══════════════════════════════════

|**Frontend (React)**|
:User selects PDF/DOCX (up to 50MB)
Chooses: Digital or Scanned + Language;

|**API (FastAPI)**|
:POST /upload
Validate file type & size;

if (Document type?) then (Digital)

  |**Services**|
  :****PyMuPDF**** extracts text
  page by page (fast, no API);

  if (Text > 500K chars?) then (Yes — Large doc)
    :Create session with
    **htoc_status = "processing"**
    Return response immediately;

    note right
      Large docs: PII runs
      in background to avoid
      upload timeout
    end note

    |**API (FastAPI)**|
    :Launch **background task**
    (same as scanned path below);

    |**Frontend (React)**|
    :Poll /htoc-status every 3s
    Show pipeline progress;

  else (No — Small doc)
    |**Services**|
    :****Presidio + spaCy**** PII detection
    12 Indian recognizers (Aadhaar, PAN, etc.)
    Replace real names → [PERSON_1], [ORG_1];

    :Create session with text + PII mapping
    **htoc_status = "building"**;

    |**Frontend (React)**|
    :Upload returns instantly
    Poll for HTOC readiness;
  endif

else (Scanned)

  |**API (FastAPI)**|
  :Quick page count via PyMuPDF
  Create session immediately
  **htoc_status = "processing"**
  Return response;

  |**Frontend (React)**|
  :Poll /htoc-status every 3s
  Show pipeline progress;

  |**Services**|
  note right
    All steps run in
    **background task**
  end note

  :****EasyOCR**** (local, CPU)
  Per-page parallel processing
  Skip blank pages (variance check)
  English: skip pages with digital text
  Non-English: OCR every page;

  :****Presidio**** PII Anonymization
  Chunked + parallel for large docs;

endif

' ═══════════════════════════════════
' HTOC + BM25 BUILD (shared path)
' ═══════════════════════════════════

|**Services**|
:====
**HTOC Build** (background);

if (Pages ≤ 3?) then (Yes)
  :Simple tree — no LLM call
  (title + page range only);
else (No)
  |**External**|
  :****Gemini 2.5 Flash****
  Analyze page previews
  Generate hierarchical TOC
  with summaries per section;
endif

|**Services**|
:**BM25 Index** build
Tokenize pages + HTOC metadata
Okapi BM25 scoring ready;

|**External**|
:Save to MongoDB **sessions**
htoc_tree + bm25_data
**htoc_status = "ready"**;

|**Frontend (React)**|
:Poll detects **ready**
Advance to Analysis stage;

' ═══════════════════════════════════
' FLOW 3: ANALYSIS
' ═══════════════════════════════════

|**Frontend (React)**|
:Auto-trigger POST /analyze;

|**API (FastAPI)**|
:Load session from MongoDB;

|**Services**|
:**TreeSearch** builds structured context
Walk HTOC → extract key sections
Cap at 25K chars (sentence boundary);

|**External**|
:****Gemini 2.5 Flash**** (JSON mode)
Analyze document with risk formula
Return: summary, parties, clauses,
risks, obligations, risk score (0-100);

|**Services**|
:**De-anonymize** result
[PERSON_1] → real name
using PII mapping;

:**Auto-save** to HistoryService
(MongoDB analysis_history);

|**Frontend (React)**|
:Display **Analysis Dashboard**
Risk score ring, clauses, risks
parties, obligations, missing clauses;

' ═══════════════════════════════════
' FLOW 4: CHAT (Vectorless RAG)
' ═══════════════════════════════════

|**Frontend (React)**|
:User asks a question
e.g. "What is the notice period?";

|**API (FastAPI)**|
:POST /chat/stream
Anonymize question via PII mapping;

|**Services**|
:**Step 1 — BM25 Keyword Search**
Tokenize query → score pages
Return top-5 pages + confidence;

if (BM25 confidence?) then (High)
  :Use BM25 context directly;
else (Low)
  :**Step 2 — LLM Tree Search**
  Send query + HTOC summaries
  to Gemini;

  |**External**|
  :Gemini reasons over HTOC
  Selects 2-5 most relevant sections
  Returns node IDs + reasoning;

  |**Services**|
  :Extract page text for
  selected HTOC nodes;
endif

|**Services**|
:Merge context from search
(pages with section headers);

|**External**|
:****Gemini 2.5 Flash**** (streaming)
Answer grounded in document context
Cite clauses, pages, sections;

|**Services**|
:**De-anonymize** response
[PERSON_1] → real name;

|**Frontend (React)**|
:Stream response token-by-token
Show source sections sidebar
User can ask follow-ups ↩;

' ═══════════════════════════════════
' FLOW 5: PDF REPORT
' ═══════════════════════════════════

|**Frontend (React)**|
:User clicks "Download Report";

|**API (FastAPI)**|
:GET /analyze/report;

|**Services**|
:**ReportGenerator**
Jinja2 template + WeasyPrint
Render analysis as styled PDF;

|**Frontend (React)**|
:Download PDF file;

stop

legend bottom
  **Privacy:** All PII processing is local (Presidio + spaCy). No personal data sent to Gemini.
  **Zero Retention:** Sessions auto-expire after 2 hours (MongoDB TTL index).
  **Vectorless RAG:** No embeddings or vector DB — uses HTOC tree + BM25 keywords.
endlegend

@enduml
